            <div class = "Install">
                <h2 id = "Inst"> Installation Guide for OCBC Digital</h2>
                <p>Please ensure that you have the OCBC Digital application on your mobile phone. If you have not, please click on the relevant images below to download</p>
                <a href = "https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ocbc.mobile&hl=en&gl=US" style="width: 20px;"><img src  ="/images//For-Logos/to_google_play_store.png" width="180" height="70"></a><a href = "https://apps.apple.com/sg/app/ocbc-digital-mobile-banking/id292506828"><img src="/images/For-Logos/to_apple_store.png" width="180" height="60"></a>
              </div>
              <div class = "registration">
                <h2 id = "reg"> Registration </h2>
                <p>Please and launch the OCBC Digital application on your mobile phone</p>
    
                <p>If it is newly installed on your device, the main page should look like this</p>
                <img src = "/images//OCBC_Digital_Pics/OCBC_Mainpage.jpg" width = "300"><br><br>
    
                <p>Click on "Sing up as a new customer" if you are a new customer</p>
                <img src = "/images//OCBC_Digital_Pics/OCBC_Mainpage_new.jpg"width = "300"><br><br>
    
                <p>click on "Local with SingPass App" if you are a local and "Foreigner with e-passport" if you are a foreigner</p>
                <img src = "/images//OCBC_Digital_Pics/OCBC_signup.jpg"width = "300"><br><br>
    
                <p>It should lead you to their website where you can choose the type of account you would like to apply for</p>
                <img src = "/images//OCBC_Digital_Pics/OCBC_selectacc.jpg"width = "300"><br><br>
    
                <p>For this guide, we will be using "360 Account"</p>
                <img src = "/images//OCBC_Digital_Pics/OCBC_selectacc_360.jpg"width = "300"><br><br>
    
                <p>Here are the benefits and requirements to apply for the account</p>
                <img src = "/images//OCBC_Digital_Pics/OCBC_360acc.jpg"width = "300">         <img src = "/images//OCBC_Digital_Pics/OCBC_360_req.jpg"width = "300"><br><br>
    
                <p>If this is the account you would like to apply for, click on the big red "Apply Online" button</p>
                <img src = "/images//OCBC_Digital_Pics/OCBC_360acc_apply.jpg"width = "300"><br><br>
    
                <p>Click on "Apply with MyInfo", then follow the instructions provided </p>
                <img src = "/images//OCBC_Digital_Pics/OCBC_apply.jpg"width = "300"><br><br>
              </div>
              <div class = "login">
                <h2 id = "Login">Login</h2>
                <p>If the OCBC Digital application is freshly installed on your device the home screen should look like this</p>
                <img src = "/images//OCBC_Digital_Pics/OCBC_Mainpage.jpg"width = "300"><br><br>
    
                <p>If you have an account with OCBC, click on "Login as existing Customer"</p>
                <img src = "/images//OCBC_Digital_Pics/OCBC_Mainpage_existing.jpg"width = "300"><br><br>
    
                <p> It should lead you to this page, click on whichever is relevant to your login</p>
                <img src = "/images//OCBC_Digital_Pics/OCBC_existing.jpg"width = "300"><br><br>
              </div>


